            "id": 5900943,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數上漲172.26點至5920.03點，漲幅3%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間14日01:00，恆生科技指數上漲172.26點（或3%），暫報5920.03點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-5.29%</li><li>近 1 月：+9.79%</li><li>近 3 月：+28.31%</li><li>近 6 月：+65.18%</li><li>今年以來：+28.64%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>乳製品概念領漲+6.20%。其中    中國飛鶴(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06186:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06186\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06186-HK</a>)            上漲        14.67%            ;        蒙牛乳業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02319:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02319\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02319-HK</a>)            上漲        8.04%            ;        澳優(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01717:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01717\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01717-HK</a>)            上漲        6.02%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大中華區概念領漲+4.67%。其中    ＦＬ二南方國指(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07288:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07288\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07288-HK</a>)            上漲        6.31%            ;        ＸＬ二南方滬深三(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07233:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07233\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07233-HK</a>)            上漲        6.07%            ;        ＸＬ二南方恒科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:07226:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/07226\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">07226-HK</a>)            上漲        5.87%    。</p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5900943",
